## Reference Index (Open only when triggered)

### Microsoft 365 / Outlook / Email / Calendar
**Trigger:** Outlook, email, inbox, calendar, Microsoft 365, Exchange, Graph.
**Action:** Use `skill_find` to locate and load the appropriate skill.

### Skill Discovery Preflight
**Trigger:** Finding, editing, or using skills.
**Action:** Use `skill_find "<keyword>"` first. Lazy-vault: `~/.opencode-lazy-vault`. Always-available: conductor, osgrep, git-push, perplexity-search. Load with `skill_use "<name>"` (underscores, not hyphens).

### File Tool Path Format Errors
**Trigger:** "Invalid path format" error
**Reference:** `docs\troubleshooting\active\file-tool-path-format-errors.md`

### ClickUp Meeting Notes
**Trigger:** "create meeting notes", "add notes to ClickUp"
**Reference:** `docs\workflows\clickup-meeting-notes.md`

### Git Commits & Pull Requests
**Trigger:** "push to GitHub", "create a commit", "make a PR"
**Action:** Use /git-push command or `docs\workflows\git-pr.md`

### Firebase Deploy Requests
**Trigger:** deploy, ship, release, go live
**Action:** Load `firebase-deployment-specialist` skill first. Set `GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS` and verify with `firebase projects:list`.

### Developer Guidelines
**Trigger:** Creating/modifying agents, commands, or skills
**Reference:** `~/.config/opencode/agent-development-standards.md`, `command-development-standards.md`, `skill-writer/SKILL.md`

### Skill Listing Format
**Trigger:** "what skills do you have?"
**Format:** Categorized list with emojis (Content Creation, Visuals, Development, Productivity, Research)

### Fully Qualified File Paths for User Review
**Always provide fully qualified absolute Windows paths** when asking user to review files.

### Public-Safe Redaction for Sharing
**Redact internal paths, IDs, and tokens** when sharing outside local contexts.

### Research Tool Fallback
**If google_search fails, fall back to** `perplexity-search` skill.

### Admin Elevation
**Trigger:** `Access is denied`, `0x80070005`
**See:** `references/admin-elevation-gsudo.md`

### Gemini Proxy Infrastructure
**Trigger:** `ECONNREFUSED 127.0.0.1:8000`, 429 errors
**See:** `references/gemini-proxy-infrastructure.md`